{"tid":1029656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六千多名非本地畢業生三年內留港就業獲居留權","createTime":"2019-02-20T11:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T12:04:53.000Z","uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a458ecd6b630a8a3f77a6a0c8299c22ff5a5a002","tid":1029656,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【Now新聞台】保安局文件顯示，過去三年共有六千多人，透過非本地畢業生留港或回港就業安排計劃，取得香港的居留權。<br />\n<br />\n根據現行計劃，非本地學生在香港修讀學士學位或更高資歷課程，畢業後六個月內可以申請留港尋找工作，或者六個月後獲得聘用，申請回港工作。<br />\n<br />\n保安局文件顯示，過去三年因為參與以上計劃獲得香港居留權的人數逐年上升，2016年有1979人、2017年有2172人，增加至去年有2455人，保安局未有提供當中多少是內地人。<br />\n<br />\n而去年有關計劃的申請人數就有10200多宗，當中逾九成八獲批，超過九成是內地人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，過去三年有超過11000名內地學生以留港就學為理由，申請延期逗留。"},{"pid":"40cc9f6efb4ff801aa7de40ba387fd13888390af","tid":1029656,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=338238\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338238&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8w6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=d78b4f0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338238&h=0b9c52a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=338238</a>"},{"pid":"fa572aaaa92d9d00b4139286bd8b8ac6d1002f23","tid":1029656,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:38:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a49b6a4c533b9e8fb065cea485ec32d8ef171036","tid":1029656,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"邊只150個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26aaa22cfdad986575fb71c7bb275eb